sources.title: Chinatown After Dark
sources.description: A female head of a Chinatown crime syndicate will use any lethal means available to acquire a valuable jewel.

sources.title: Chinatown After Dark (1931) PRE-CODE HOLLYWOOD
sources.description:
Stars: Carmel Myers, Rex Lease, Barbara Kent 
 Director: Stuart Paton

 The female head of a criminal gang in Chinatown is after a valuable jewel, and lets nothing stand in her way of finding it.

sources.description:
See what happens in the underworld dens after dark!  The female head of a criminal gang in Chinatown is after a valuable jewel, and lets nothing stand in her way of finding it.
